So I modified Katrik's game by adding a little dude you control with the mouse cursor. He doddles along trying to follow your mouse cursor and eats all balls that bump into him. As he gets fatter he gets slower so you'd better prioritize the order of balls before he gets too slow!

From: http://yapgh.blogspot.com/2010/02/quick-game-for-toronto-perl-mongers.html

To play this game you need the following:

    * Only for Linux) sudo apt-get install libsdl-dev libsdl_gfx-dev
    * cpan Alien::SDL
    * Click Download Source http://github.com/kthakore/SDL_perl/tree/redesign
    * Extract it
    * perl Build.PL; perl Build; perl Build install
    * perl Shooter.pl

